text.__SUMMARY__:
Inga neblinensis is a species of legume in the family Fabaceae.
It is found only in Venezuela.
text.Sources: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Inga neblinensis". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T38278A10104725. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T38278A10104725.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
